Package com.tangosol.net.topic

Interface Subscriber.Element<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of value stored in the topic
    Enclosing interface:
    Subscriber<V>
    public static interface Subscriber.Element<V>
    Element represents a container for returned values.
